# Package-local hygiene for The Fiction Adaptation submission package.
# LibreOffice / OpenOffice write a temporary lock file next to any open
# document (e.g. .~lock.My-File.docx#). Because the repo-root .gitignore
# ignores any `exports/` directory, the export DOCX must be force-added —
# and a blanket `git add -f exports/` would otherwise sweep these lock
# files in. Ignore them here so that can't happen.
.~lock.*#

# Belt-and-braces: never want OS cruft in the package either.
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
